! Numeric golden test for the RAYTRA2 real-ray path (optimization/tolerancing).
! Call chain: CAPFN -> COMPAP (WAVSPOT5.f90:1932) -> CALL RAYTRA2 (RAYTRA5.f90:2832)
! RMSOPD and PTOVOPD scalars are computed directly from RAYTRA2 ray coordinates,
! so any regression in RAYTRA2 will produce a golden diff here.

RES osdtriplet

! --- On-axis field ---
FOB 0
CAPFN
SHO RMSOPD
SHO PTOVOPD

! --- Mid-field ---
FOB 0.7
CAPFN
SHO RMSOPD
SHO PTOVOPD

! --- Full field ---
FOB 1.0
CAPFN
SHO RMSOPD
SHO PTOVOPD
